Notes 2023-05-12

About the game over music:

The game over music is going to be inspired by Jack Stauber's "We see you, Opal (Reprise)". A simple melody that evolves and evolves and suddenly ends with an important leitmotiv, which is going to be used in the music for Scene - Bad ending.
This leitmotiv will only appear in game overs, so, basically when you game over, like losing a battle or a minigame or something like that, and, in the bad ending.

We see you, Opal (Reprise) - Jack Stauber:
